name: Modal V-Neck 3/4 Dolman
short_description:
A KALECO customer favourite!


3/4 dolman sleeve v-neck top in ecological premium quality modal span jersey; super soft and fashionably comfy. Made by Natural Life with premium quality USA knitted fabrications and garments made in USA.


They use Lenzing Modal and Micro Modal (branded fibers), which are naturally soft on the skin and exceptionally ecological.

name: To The Mountains T-Shirt
short_description:
Just get me out of this next zoom meeting!

This classic tee is made from a sustainable blend of organic and recycled materials that’s easy on the planet and all the mountains.


  • Regular Fit
  • Short sleeve crewneck t-shirt, ribbed neck, linework graphic
  • 45% Recycled Polyester, 30% TENCEL™ Lyocell, 25% Organic Cotton
  • Wash cold, hang dry
  • Designed in Canada, ethically made in China
